Fit-Time, Training and Search By HBM Edison, Ltd
Fit-Time is a New Tab Chrome Extension providing a variety of fit and health content that will help you building the perfect workouts and an accessible web search (provided by Bing.com) right in the comfort of your web browser.

The search features use within the extension will be provided by Bing; however, the extension will not make any changes in your default browser search setting.
